---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import MuizzImage from "../assets/muizz.jpeg"
import SocialLinks from "./SocialLinks.astro"
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro"
import WorkTag from "./WorkTag.astro"
import Code from "./Code.astro"
---

<header class="flex flex-col gap-8">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <div
      class="relative flex size-24 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-full border border-white shadow-md shadow-slate-200"
    >
      <Image
        alt="Olayiwola"
        class="block aspect-square h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
        src={MuizzImage}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-1">
      <div>
        <h1 class="flex scroll-m-20 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          Karaole Olayiwola
        </h1>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">
          <p>Backend developer based in Lagos, Nigeria.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <WorkTag />
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="space-y-2">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <SectionTitle>About Me</SectionTitle>
      <p class="leading-7 text-slate-500">
        I am a backend engineer with over 5 years of experience, primarily working with PHP Laravel and Python Django. I specialize in building robust, scalable systems, with additional expertise in automation, bot development, and both consuming and creating REST APIs.

Recently, I’ve expanded my skillset by picking up the MERN stack, allowing me to bridge front-end and back-end development when necessary, though my focus remains on backend architecture. I have experience working with various tech stacks, particularly JavaScript, and I’m proficient in hosting and deployment.

While my front-end design knowledge is limited, I’m passionate about creating efficient backend solutions that drive smooth and functional user experiences.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-7 text-slate-500">
        I recently completed <a
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-sm underline underline-offset-2 outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-slate-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
          href="https://www.shopsintel.com/"
          >Shopsintel <i data-lucide="external-link" class="size-3 text-slate-400"
          ></i></a
        >, a TikTok Shop tool designed for discovering trending products, live creators, and analyzing competitor shops. This platform allows users to gain insights into the dynamic world of TikTok commerce, helping them stay ahead of trends and competitors. I was responsible for both the development and optimization of the platform, ensuring it met user needs and performed efficiently..<br
        />The project was built using <Code>PHP</Code> with 
        <Code>Laravel</Code> serving as the main framework. I utilized
        <Code>tailwind </Code>
        <Code>@css </Code>for the front-end, ensuring a smooth and responsive design, while
        <Code>MySQL</Code> handled the data storage and management. For admin interfaces and internal tools, I leveraged 
        <Code>Filament</Code>  allowing for fast and elegant user interaction with the system..
      </p>

      <SocialLinks />
    </div>
  </section>
</header>
